about:
Hi, we are Douwe and Niki, how are you doing?

Together, with many other enthusiast young people from Amsterdam, we are KeyOkay, a company specialized in short stay renting out apartments in  Amsterdam, Antwerp and Florence!

What we do
Everything we do, we believe to bring people authentic value and story telling together!& We manage properties with the care and dedication (so with a high service/quality level and a personal touch) you deserves !!

 By taking over everything involved, like handing over keys, cleaning the apartment or providing clean sheets, we can provide our customers a safe and convenient feeling when there are abroad on one of their many journeys. For their guests we provide the extra service a reception brings to a hotel. So we are, if necessary, available 24/7. 

Hope to meet you soon!

KeyOkay. Your house, our care.
